name: MIS Activities allocations in the past v2 NSR1529
description:
The report returns a list of prisoners, currently in the establishment and their activity attendance status for a date range. The data is shown over 4 tabs: All Attendance by Activity Service Description, by Surname and by Attendance Status. 4th tab also displays attendance comments and If a Case Note Warning entry has been issued. 5th tab display details of the Warning types. The report can be displayed by individual Wing or by all Wings.
ACT0021 - v00.00.05 Last Modified: 13/05/2017

dataset.name: Activities
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.SURNAME, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.FIRST_NAME, AT_CELL.UNIT_1_CODE, AT_CELL.UNIT_4_SHORT_DESCRIPTION, nvl(AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.IEP_BAND,'** Incentive Level Missing **'), AT_DIM_PROGRAMME_SERVICE.DESCRIPTION, AT_DIM_PROGRAMME_TYPE.DESCRIPTION, AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.SUSPENDED_FLAG, TRUNC(AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.START_TIME), nvl(AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.SLOT_CATEGORY_CODE,'No Slot'), DT_CURRENT_RELEASE_DATE.CURR_RELEASE_DATE, AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.COMMENT_TEXT, AT_DIM_ACTIVITY_STATUS.DESCRIPTION, AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.SLOT_CATEGORY_CODE FROM BODIMIS.FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY, BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP, BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT AT_ACTIVITY_ESTABLISHMENT, BODIMIS.DIM_OFFENDER_BOOKING AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING, BODIMIS.DIM_CELL AT_CELL, BODIMIS.DIM_PROGRAMME_SERVICE AT_DIM_PROGRAMME_SERVICE, BODIMIS.DIM_PROGRAMME_TYPE AT_DIM_PROGRAMME_TYPE, (   Select AT_FACT_OFFENDER_SENTENCE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK as OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK, case when AT_RELEASE_DATE.DAY_DATE <> '31/12/9000' Then AT_RELEASE_DATE.DAY_DATE end as CURR_RELEASE_DATE From --BODIMIS.FACT_CASE_SENTENCE AT_FACT_SENTENCE, BODIMIS.FACT_OFFENDER_SENTENCE AT_FACT_OFFENDER_SENTENCE, BODIMIS.DIM_DATE AT_RELEASE_DATE where --AT_FACT_OFFENDER_SENTENCE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK=AT_FACT_SENTENCE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK(+) AT_FACT_OFFENDER_SENTENCE.RELEASE_CALCULATED_DATE_SK=AT_RELEASE_DATE.DATE_SK(+) and AT_FACT_OFFENDER_SENTENCE.SENTENCE_CURRENT_FLAG='Y' --and AT_RELEASE_DATE.DAY_DATE !='31/12/9000' ) DT_CURRENT_RELEASE_DATE, BODIMIS.DIM_REFERENCE_CODES AT_DIM_ACTIVITY_STATUS WHERE ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK=DT_CURRENT_RELEASE_DATE.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK(+) ) AND ( AT_CELL.UNIT_4_SK=AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.LIVING_UNIT_SK ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK IN (SELECT CSL.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK FROM BODIMIS.DIM_STAFF_ACCESSIBLE_CASELOAD SAC, BODIMIS.DIM_CASELOAD_SECURITY_LIST CSL WHERE SAC.CASELOAD_ID=CSL.CASELOAD_CODE AND SAC.USERNAME = UPPER((SELECT username FROM context_ /*= #Variable('BOUSER') */ )) AND CSL.ENDYEAR >= to_char(sysdate,'YYYY')-6 ) ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.ESTABLISHMENT_SK=AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ESTABLISHMENT_SK ) AND ( AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ACTIVE_FLAG='Y' ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK=AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK ) AND ( AT_DIM_PROGRAMME_TYPE.PROGRAMME_TYPE_SK=AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.PROGRAMME_TYPE_SK ) AND ( AT_DIM_ACTIVITY_STATUS.CODE_DOMAIN(+)='PS_PA_OC' ) AND ( AT_DIM_ACTIVITY_STATUS.CODE(+)=AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.STATUS ) AND ( AT_ACTIVITY_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_SK=AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.ESTABLISHMENT_SK ) AND ( AT_DIM_PROGRAMME_SERVICE.PROGRAMME_SERVICE_SK=AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.PROGRAMME_SERVICE_SK ) AND ( ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.BOOKING_STATUS = 'O' ) AND ( AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.MIS_CURRENT_RECORD_IND='Y' ) AND ( AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.ALLOCATED_FLAG = 'Y' ) AND AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK = (SELECT ESTABLISHMENT_CODE FROM prompt_ /*= #prompt('Establishment Code','A','Associated Establishment\Associated Establishment Code',Mono,Free,Not_Persistent,,User:1) */ ) AND AT_ACTIVITY_ESTABLISHMENT.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK = (SELECT ESTABLISHMENT_CODE FROM prompt_ /*= #prompt('Establishment Code','A','Activities\Activity Establishment Code',Mono,Free,Not_Persistent,,User:0) */ ) AND AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.OFFENDER_START_DATE <= (SELECT START_DATE FROM prompt_ /*= #prompt('Allocation Start Date:','D',,Mono,Free,Persistent,,User:2) */ ) AND AT_FACT_OFFENDER_ACTIVITY.OFFENDER_END_DATE >= (SELECT END_DATE FROM prompt_ /*= #prompt('Allocation End Date:','D',,Mono,Free,Persistent,,User:3) */ ) )), dataset_ AS (SELECT FROM dataset_base_)

dataset.name: MIS Load
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG.BUSINESS_DATE FROM BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG WHERE (BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG.LOAD_ID = (SELECT MAX(LOAD_ID) FROM BODIMIS.ETL_LOAD_LOG WHERE NOT LOAD_END_DATETIME IS NULL))), dataset_ AS (SELECT BUSINESS_DATE FROM dataset_base_)
